kde pracuje Hye Soo.

193
00:14:16,490 --> 00:14:17,740
Sú tam dobrí odborníci.

194
00:14:17,741 --> 00:14:19,853
- Nemocnica Hankkuk?
- Tam pracuje Hye Soo.

195
00:14:28,151 --> 00:14:29,424
Hej.

196
00:14:41,554 --> 00:14:44,429
